Klopp on fans calling for him to sign a new centre-back: &quot;That will never stop, until we do it! I love the game, but I don't think the solution is always to sign a new player.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Alberto Moreno played fantastic this season, then he played not well at Sevilla and there were people so quick to say 'that's why you need a new left-back.' Wow! Really?&quot;
